CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 13, 1973, pg. 9 reads: "To Be Honored - Mrs. Homer S. Brown will receive a special award when the NAACP of Pittsburgh sponsors its Fifth Annual Martin Luther King, Jr. Memorial Program at Schenley High School, Monday, Jan. 15, at 7:30 p.m. - Harris photos"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Wilhelmina Byrd Brown wearing dark imprint patterned blouse with round metal buttons and jeweled brooch, seated on upholstered chair with wood carved decorations
